{
  "id": "RAW_31313d",
  "title": "Claude 记忆系统逆向研究！与 ChatGPT 完全相反！网友：放弃广告了？Claude 深夜祭出记忆选项，隐身聊天，按项目单独记忆",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODI5Njc2MA==&mid=2655928882&idx=1&sn=4a8362ab05bb1aeee48faef7f0889785",
  "date": "2025-09-14 03:30:00",
  "author": "51CTO技术栈",
  "siteName": "51CTO技术栈",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">编辑 | 云昭</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"119\" data-end=\"203\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODI5Njc2MA==&amp;mid=2655928871&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=4ef74a79992f24dd9ce81a47bab2aec5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"上一篇\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">上一篇</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">文章中，小编分享了一位狠人逆向研究了 OpenAI 的 ChatGPT 底层记忆机制。它的记忆系统主要分为四个板块：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">交互元数据、最近会话内容、模型设定上下文、用户知识记忆。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"119\" data-end=\"203\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">正是基于这样的设计，才会让 ChatGPT 充满了十足的留人能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"119\" data-end=\"203\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那么，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">另一大头部的 AI 助手 Claude</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;又是怎样设计自身的记忆系统的呢？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"119\" data-end=\"203\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">昨天，Claude 的记忆系统也被逆向工程了一波，这位狠人的出的结论是：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"119\" data-end=\"203\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Claude 与 ChatGPT 走的是两种截然不同的方向。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">我又研究了 Claude，结果发现了一件很有意思的事情：这两大头部 AI 助手居然构建了完全相反的记忆系统。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">ChatGPT 是“全都要”，Claude 是每次都“从0开始”。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2490740740740741\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"508445225\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=16b9aff5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQqg9wHMIXpN0ENkEqZ7coHND4a2UvpDicnzh1x92gZOiaqviclc0BeMgU8mnjGhsLwn7ZDx83cODQ2sA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"205\" data-end=\"314\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这说明了各自的用户群体和产品哲</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">学是什么？以及 AI 记忆设计的潜力空间到底有多大。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"205\" data-end=\"314\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这篇文章中，作者首先拆解 Claude 的记忆机制——它到底存储什么、怎么取。然后，再聊更有趣的部分：为什么这两种架构会走向如此不同的道路？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"205\" data-end=\"314\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这篇文章描述的剧烈反差感，引起了网友对于 OpenAI、Anthropic 这两大 AI 超级独角兽的疯狂讨论，评论数已经多达 231 条。&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.09759036144578313\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"830\" style=\"width: 578px;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/MOwlO0INfQqg9wHMIXpN0ENkEqZ7coHNP9a9ibltKc8CicISIicV3FiaGaqctFfVicVd6dRdAPs6lWDibvSOnb5WwLzg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"830\" data-cropy2=\"81.85121107266436\" data-imgfileid=\"508445226\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d3e78f98&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FMOwlO0INfQqg9wHMIXpN0ENkEqZ7coHNwc3g2KOibIp1pQOHmbLCTZKHkn11kZjEtlQQnBuMtjCoeZmT0dl0pDQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一些网友认为这是两家公司在为未来的商业模式做铺垫：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">ChatGPT 的方向性很明确，未来他们会通过广告和联盟链接盈利。而其记忆功能旨在创建用户画像。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">而 Claude 的记忆实现感觉更侧重于访问抽象概念和过去交互的长期目标。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"205\" data-end=\"314\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但更有意思的是，这篇逆向文章刚发布不久后，昨天 Claude 似乎也看到了用户的热烈讨论，很快为 Claude 上线了新的记忆功能：专为工作团队设计！</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"205\" data-end=\"314\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"A modal dialog box titled &quot;Memory&quot; overlaid on a background of conversation topics. The modal contains two toggle options: &quot;Search and reference chats&quot; and &quot;Generate memory of chat history&quot;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"508445224\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c74130f0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FMOwlO0INfQqg9wHMIXpN0ENkEqZ7coHNnXNptZGhuYZgZE5nxkLyQJ2ttWQ5MOkecpGbM3XayQDibZa5icKXfQ8w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"508428128\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df6c4681&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvFXuhILX3JhsfmCGP3UXkY5FYq08vSDZ3iboc71BweGlL0gcgibaGG0Jw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"321\" data-end=\"339\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">Claude 的工作方式：两个基本特征</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"341\" data-end=\"363\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Claude 的记忆系统有两个基本特征：</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"367\" data-end=\"431\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"367\" data-end=\"375\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">从零开始</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：每次对话都以一张白纸开场，不会自动加载用户画像或历史记录。只有当你</span></span><strong data-start=\"411\" data-end=\"421\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">明确调用记忆</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">时，它才会启用。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"435\" data-end=\"519\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"435\" data-end=\"445\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">原始记录检索</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Claude 回忆时，只会基于你真实的对话记录，而不是依赖 AI 自动生成的摘要或压缩档案。它就像在做实时搜索，直接在你的历史聊天中查找。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p data-start=\"521\" data-end=\"667\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当 Claude 通过类似</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">&nbsp;</span></span><em data-start=\"535\" data-end=\"547\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">“我们之前聊过什么”</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">、</span></span><em data-start=\"548\" data-end=\"562\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">“从上次聊到的地方继续”</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">、</span></span><em data-start=\"563\" data-end=\"575\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">“还记得我说过……”</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这样的提示检测到你在调用记忆时，它会调动</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">两种检索工具</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"521\" data-end=\"667\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这有点像你在用网页搜索或执行代码——Claude 会现场运行搜索，你能看到它“检索中”，等完成后再综合结果来回答或继续话题。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"674\" data-end=\"703\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><strong data-start=\"678\" data-end=\"701\"> \n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"508428129\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=65f7dc56&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVv7ibyGuL0I4icm8WDcjJED18MoII9zQibicm14LThHibzUyEx9XKLuhLcbnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p> \n    <h3 data-start=\"321\" data-end=\"339\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;321&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;339&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">两种检索工具</span></span></h3> \n   </strong></h3>\n  <h3 data-start=\"674\" data-end=\"703\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><strong data-start=\"678\" data-end=\"701\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">| 1、会话检索 Conversation Search</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"705\" data-end=\"753\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><code data-start=\"705\" data-end=\"726\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">conversation_search</span></span></code><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;工具用于关键词和主题搜索，覆盖你全部的对话历史。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"755\" data-end=\"922\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">比如我问它：</span></span><em data-start=\"761\" data-end=\"798\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“能回忆一下我们聊过的有关昌德尼朝克（德里的一处历史街区）的内容吗？”</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"755\" data-end=\"922\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Claude 找到了 9 段相关对话——从我研究贾汗娜拉·贝古姆公主在 1650 年建立该区的历史，到我问哪家烤肉串（galouti kebabs）和馅饼（parathas）最好吃。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">最后 Claude 把这些零散的记录整合成了一份连贯的总结。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"755\" data-end=\"922\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Claude searching for Chandni Chowk conversations\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7472222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"508445213\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb006434&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQqQSEVgtxQwxuibLibQibRPCOibrnzV9eAxLy2a6AVXVrFoxxTVqP3DWtAcHicbynuOrCibm6hY0aibqOImg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"1138\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">如果你一次问多个主题，Claude 会依次进行多次搜索</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。比如我在做加密研究时，常用 Claude 做编辑。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"1138\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有次我问它：</span></span><em data-start=\"983\" data-end=\"1030\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“能告诉我我们聊过的关于米开朗基罗、Chainflip 或 Solana 的所有对话吗？”</span></span></em></p>\n  <p data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"1138\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">ps：在区块链和加密领域，常见的项目名字经常会会借用艺</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">术家、神话人物；</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: normal;\">后面的&nbsp;</span></span><em data-start=\"983\" data-end=\"1030\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;924&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;1138&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;em&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;983&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;1030&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: normal;\">Chainflip 或 Solana 是两个加密项目。</span></span></em></p>\n  <p data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"1138\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Claude 就分别跑了三次搜索：一次找我把米开朗基罗类比神经网络的内容，一次找 Chainflip 的跨链协议，一次找 Solana 的技术架构。最后一共找出 22 段对话，并生成了一个带跳转链接的统一回答。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"1138\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Claude running multiple searches for different topics\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7129629629629629\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"508445214\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2e512b2a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQqQSEVgtxQwxuibLibQibRPCOib6V3QegyfIXdLI37xjicomsp3aNY9hGnZ4Mdd8zrAPVptO36DSPibmG8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1145\" data-end=\"1178\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;\"><strong data-start=\"1149\" data-end=\"1176\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">| 2、短期对话检索 Temporal Chat Retrieval&nbsp;</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1210\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><code data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1194\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">recent_chats</span></span></code><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;工具提供按时间检索的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1212\" data-end=\"1271\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我问它：</span></span><em data-start=\"1216\" data-end=\"1239\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“能告诉我最近 10 次对话聊了什么吗？”</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;Claude 就按时间顺序把最近的聊天抓出来，并做了总结。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1212\" data-end=\"1271\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Claude retrieving last 10 conversations\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7277777777777777\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"508445215\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=23607d49&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQqQSEVgtxQwxuibLibQibRPCOibGAq3a1iaqdniay2hAxJECyOkcnxLu5MiasRlqffjbtmn5fW1K3u6icyWgg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1273\" data-end=\"1348\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它还可以指定时间段。比如我问：</span></span><em data-start=\"1288\" data-end=\"1320\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“能告诉我 2024 年 11 月最后一周我们聊过什么吗？”</span></span></em><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;Claude 就找出了那段时间里的 16 个对话。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1355\" data-end=\"1382\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><strong data-start=\"1359\" data-end=\"1380\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Claude retrieving conversations from November 2024\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"508445216\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e767d86b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQqQSEVgtxQwxuibLibQibRPCOibgibJ4BJFzVZYjXpWdqicpoyK1nn8QAw9LfW5urTL45AT9yFibbqC7PfgQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></strong></h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"508428131\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d876485&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvxSHbjbhmqPxCwjQ6qqBkHI3m9IDoV0x2pqqY78zMd9eu5sA4ee0KCQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1355\" data-end=\"1382\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><strong data-start=\"1359\" data-end=\"1380\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">ChatGPT向左：用户无需思考的魔法</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1355\" data-end=\"1382\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><strong data-start=\"1359\" data-end=\"1380\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">&nbsp;Claude向右：让用户自己控制调用时机</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"1384\" data-end=\"1450\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">时间回到一年前，ChatGPT 和 Claude 的功能几乎是对齐的——多模型、文件上传、项目管理都有。但从那以后，两者的路线分化明显。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 0px;margin-right: 0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1653\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1465\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ChatGPT</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：已经演变为一个大众级消费产品。OpenAI 的 CPO Mike Krieger 也承认他们在用户增长上“抓住了闪电”。记忆上，ChatGPT 走的是全自动化：所有记忆组件都会自动加载，用户无需思考，就能得到个性化体验。这意味着它会逐渐构建详细的用户画像，学习偏好与模式，为未来功能或商业化打基础。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">这是典型的消费级科技思路</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：做得足够“魔法”，用户黏住，之后再想办法变现。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1657\" data-end=\"1850\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"1657\" data-end=\"1667\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Claude</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：走的是另一条路，聚焦开发者工具、编程和专业工作流。Anthropic 的用户群体更技术化，他们理解 LLM 的运作方式，也习惯</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">自己控制调用的时机</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。就像他们会手动选择</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">是否触发网页搜索或“扩展思考”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">他们也决定什么时候需要记忆</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。用户知道调用记忆会增加延迟，但他们愿意做这种权衡。他们要的不是持续画像，而是一个强大、可预测的专业工具。而且，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;background-color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">这类用户往往对隐私更敏感</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"508428133\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2e356694&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvlydibLicaBC57FUZw91MhHHCNmBlamtdImWmImY9u5Yzw0SlcdNLnb5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1857\" data-end=\"1874\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><strong data-start=\"1861\" data-end=\"1872\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">记忆的设计空间，没有唯一解</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"1876\" data-end=\"1962\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">令人震撼的是：ChatGPT 和 Claude 这两大头部AI助手，居然构建了完全相反的记忆系统。这说明&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"1927\" data-end=\"1960\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI 记忆的设计空间极其巨大，没有所谓的“唯一正确答案”。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1964\" data-end=\"2002\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">设计记忆系统时，你必须从用户出发，根据他们的需求倒推，然后从零开始构建。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2004\" data-end=\"2163\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更关键的是，我们还处于未开垦的领域</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">。这些工具问世还不到三年，没人知道如果同一个人用 AI 助手十年会怎样。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2004\" data-end=\"2163\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">它应该记多少？要怎么处理累积多年的上下文？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2004\" data-end=\"2163\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与此同时，市面上正爆发出“寒武纪式”的 AI 应用，每家都在实验自己的记忆方式，而底层模型还在快速迭代。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2004\" data-end=\"2163\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而在应用侧，同样没有固定的打法，也没有最佳实践——大家都在试、在看：究竟谁能跑出来。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2165\" data-end=\"2246\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，原本是想研究记忆系统，结果却慢慢地牵扯出产品层面的思考。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/MOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvWXnSu9Q4wStccUsIJfVTNK1OfmxCNJAoXH8qTiaUtWgsiaGBo97KdhoQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"73\" data-imgfileid=\"508428132\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ac2d0dd8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvWXnSu9Q4wStccUsIJfVTNK1OfmxCNJAoXH8qTiaUtWgsiaGBo97KdhoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"403\" data-end=\"418\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">几小时后：Claude 放出了新的记忆功能</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"419\" data-end=\"546\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就在昨天晚上，作者发表了逆向文章后的几个小时后，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Anthropic 就宣布，Claude 正式上线&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"158\" data-end=\"174\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">记忆（Memory）功能。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">不过，一个关键的信号是：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">团队和企业用户可以率先体验。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23055555555555557\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"508445228\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=36d998f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQqg9wHMIXpN0ENkEqZ7coHNmeDPnW2zJwDuTDRgd3dD9NePL4Iib2o06LK7GI8IaWvFXGxrLLmUJmQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"419\" data-end=\"546\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这项功能可以在“设置”中启用。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">包含两个开关选项：“搜索并引用聊天记录”和“生成聊天历史记忆”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"419\" data-end=\"546\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">来看一看，Claude 新发布的记忆功能的主要用途：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"360\" data-end=\"382\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">记住团队流程、客户需求、项目细节和优先级</span></span></p>\n    <p data-start=\"419\" data-end=\"546\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;419&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;546&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">比如，销售团队能在不同交易中保持客户上下文，产品团队能在多轮迭代中延续产品规格，高管则能跟踪各项战略举措，而无需不断重建背景信息。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"385\" data-end=\"410\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">支持为</span></span><strong data-start=\"388\" data-end=\"401\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">每个项目单独建记忆</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，避免信息混杂</span></span></p>\n    <p data-start=\"548\" data-end=\"673\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;548&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;673&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">这确保了产品发布规划与客户项目相互分离，机密讨论不会与日常运营混杂。这样的项目边界能帮助你和团队同时管理多个复杂任务，而不至于混淆不相关的信息，相当于一层保护栏，确保敏感对话得到隔离。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"508445229\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4006ec79&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQqg9wHMIXpN0ENkEqZ7coHNtJAP4IBiaicqzl6Dsorh4z0QjWI8LNhWnHtQy09sicrSl7EuwkAKoW90g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"413\" data-end=\"447\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">通过</span></span><strong data-start=\"415\" data-end=\"423\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">记忆摘要</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，用户可随时查看和编辑 Claude 的记忆</span></span></p>\n    <p data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"826\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;710&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;826&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Claude 会通过“记忆摘要”来整合所有记忆，供你查看和编辑。在设置中，可以清楚看到 Claude 从你的对话中记住了哪些内容，并能随时通过与 Claude 对话更新摘要。根据你的指令，Claude 会调整所引用的记忆内容。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"449\" data-end=\"480\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，在官方介绍中，Anthropic 特别强调了企业用户的控制权和隐私安全：</span></span></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"533\" data-end=\"570\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"533\" data-end=\"541\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可选开启</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：用户可以自由决定 Claude 记住什么、不记住什么</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"573\" data-end=\"612\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"573\" data-end=\"581\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">隐身聊天</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：提供“一次性对话”，不会进入记忆或历史，非常适合敏感讨论</span></span></p>\n    <p data-start=\"844\" data-end=\"995\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;844&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;995&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">有时候，用户需要 Claude 的帮助，但又不想使用或增加记忆。这时就可以用隐身聊天，它提供了一张干净的对话“白纸”。这种模式非常适合敏感的头脑风暴、机密的战略讨论，或是单纯想要一次不带上下文的新对话。你的常规记忆和历史对话不会受到影响。如果你在团队版或企业版中使用记忆，标准的数据保留策略依然适用。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6703703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"508445230\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=352d5bb1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQqg9wHMIXpN0ENkEqZ7coHNtGRP4yBdy9Mr0u0Tib1DaX6pL8bD5jJlk49wkz79Ipj8LtOlOplYeUA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"615\" data-end=\"643\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"615\" data-end=\"623\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">企业管理</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：管理员可随时关闭整个组织的记忆功能</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"419\" data-end=\"546\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">总之，通过“Memory”功能，Claude 会专注于学习用户的职业背景和工作模式，从而最大化生产力。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"826\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这里需要注意，记忆功能也带来了新的安全考量，所以 Anthropic 在设计时，强调：确保它适用于工作场景，同时避免涉及敏感话题。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"710\" data-end=\"826\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">官方博客中表示：Claude 团队将采取</span></span><strong data-start=\"1124\" data-end=\"1135\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">循序渐进的方式</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，以负责任的方式部署这些强大功能，并持续评估和测试记忆在不同使用场景中的表现，再逐步扩大适用范围。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 2 []\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"508428132\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ac2d0dd8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvWXnSu9Q4wStccUsIJfVTNK1OfmxCNJAoXH8qTiaUtWgsiaGBo97KdhoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"2165\" data-end=\"2246\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">OpenAI和Anthropic为什么走了相反的路？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"47\" data-end=\"126\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">乍看之下，两者路线还是比较清晰的。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">最基本的区别：ChatGPT 想记住你这个人，而 Claude 关心的是企业用户之前的交互。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"47\" data-end=\"126\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，OpenAI 更像是打造一款AI时代的万能微信，而 Anthropic 则避其锋芒，专门瞄准企业服务领域，所以更像是“企业钉钉”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"47\" data-end=\"126\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一位网友认为，Anthropic 和 OpenAI 的区别可能更多体现在商业目标上，而不是技术本身。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"47\" data-end=\"126\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">ChatGPT 的方向很明确：最终会通过广告和返佣链接来变现。他们的记忆实现方式，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">核心就是在建立用户画像</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"128\" data-end=\"323\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Claude 的记忆实现更像是面向长期目标，关注的是如何访问抽象概念和过往交互。这很接近人类回忆的方式，只是多了个搜索功能（据我所知他们还没真正实现）。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"128\" data-end=\"323\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有网友认为，Claude 的路线很清晰：以后可以结合 RL 后训练，让 Claude “记住”你上次指出的错误。在未来的迭代里，它甚至能从对话中提炼出抽象，比如“用户上次让我在这个任务里改了某些地方，也许这次我可以主动做”或者“上次代理是这样完成这个任务的”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"403\" data-end=\"433\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不过，小编判断，Anthropic 或许不会放弃个性化广告这个已相对成熟的商业模式的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"403\" data-end=\"433\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">评论区的大佬们，你们又是如何看待的呢？欢迎拍砖。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"403\" data-end=\"433\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://www.shloked.com/writing/claude-memory\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.shloked.com/writing/claude-memory</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/news/memory\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.anthropic.com/news/memory</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章逆向分析了 Claude 与 ChatGPT 记忆系统的根本差异，并介绍了 Claude 最新上线的、面向企业用户的高度可控记忆功能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章逆向分析了 Claude 与 ChatGPT 记忆系统的根本差异，并介绍了 Claude 最新上线的、面向企业用户的高度可控记忆功能。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了 AI 助手 Claude 与 ChatGPT 在记忆系统设计上的截然不同哲学。ChatGPT 倾向于自动化、全面记录用户交互以构建用户画像，服务于消费级市场；而 Claude 则秉持“从零开始”和“原始记录检索”原则，赋予用户高度控制权，更侧重于开发者工具和专业工作流。文章详细阐述了 Claude 的会话检索和短期对话检索两种记忆工具。此外，文章还报道了 Claude 在逆向研究发布后不久，即上线了面向团队和企业用户的全新记忆功能，包括项目独立记忆、记忆摘要、隐身聊天和企业管理权限，进一步强化其在企业服务领域的定位。这反映出 AI 记忆设计空间的巨大多样性，以及产品策略对技术实现路径的深刻影响。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Claude 与 ChatGPT 的记忆系统设计哲学完全相反",
      "explanation": "ChatGPT 偏向自动全面记忆以构建用户画像并实现商业化，而 Claude 则强调从零开始、用户显式控制和原始记录检索，聚焦专业和企业用户需求。"
    },
    {
